this theory predicts a Maxwellian distribution\nin pre-collapse core rotation frequency that is uncorrelated with the spin of\nthe overlying envelope.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Feb 2015 22:31:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 23 Jul 2015 20:23:17 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 4 Sep 2015 22:25:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-08"}
