 it in the parameter space of rings and transit config-\nuration. We discuss the prospects of using this method for the first systematic\nsearch of exoplanetary rings in the Kepler database and provide a basic\ncomputational code for implementing it.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Feb 2015 05:47:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 15 Apr 2015 20:03:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-04-17"}
